Modules
Testcase categories

The following categories are part of the Trustonic Integration Tests. More...

Modules

 Manual
 This category gathers manual testcases.
 
 Quick
 This category subset gathers testcases ensure that Trustonic TEE is installed, running, and accessible (less than 1 minute run-time).
 
 Basic
 This category subset gathers testcases that provide a quick (less than 5 minutes) verification of the Trustonic TEE integration.
 
 Extensive
 This category gathers testcases that provide an extensive validation of the integration (~1.5 hours execution time) must be run on commercial devices.
 
 Final Device
 This category gathers testcases that must be run on final commercial devices (~1.5 hours execution time).
 
 Trustonic Test Suite
 This category gathers all testcases that are included in Trustonic Test Suite (external)GP

 
 Not tagged
 Here are listed the testcases that do not have any category tag (the test executable must be launched without filters specified for them to run).
 

Detailed Description
